node.text:
Huge thank you to @PaniniAmerica for selecting me to be one of their first college athlete partners. Looking forward to getting some signed memorabilia in your hands! #NIL 

Excited to officially announce our exclusive memorabilia partnership. We’re just getting started! 

#PaniniNIL
